bottom that's down here at the bottom,

00:03:53.620 --> 00:03:54.840
for example.

00:03:55.410 --> 00:03:59.040
And bring up the leaderboard UI.

00:03:59.060 --> 00:04:01.480
And, okay, this is all fine.

00:04:01.480 --> 00:04:05.490
